      "title": "Read the remarks",
      "sections": [
        {
          "number": 1,
          "heading": "George",
          "text": "I'm just not feeling very happy today. Everything seems to have gone wrong."
        },
        {
          "number": 2,
          "heading": "Katie",
          "text": "I like my life and I have nothing to complain about."
        },
        {
          "number": 3,
          "heading": "Pilar",
          "text": "I felt so good that nothing bad had happened. It could have been a disaster."
        },
        {
          "number": 4,
          "heading": "Max",
          "text": "I've had enough of all the arguments and the bad atmosphere at work."
        },
        {
          "number": 5,
          "heading": "Agnes",
          "text": "I felt very happy when I heard she had an interview for the job."
        },
        {
          "number": 6,
          "heading": "Sara",
          "text": "Thank you for helping me today."
        },
        {
          "number": 7,
          "heading": "Carlos",
